@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ryvzpp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.21
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.49) + (v1 + 0.55 - v0 + 0.40)) * (0.05 / (tmp + 0.30 - v1 + 0.42)))
    v2 = ((tmp * v2) - (tmp + wp.exp(tmp + 0.27)))
    data[tid] = v0
